<h2>Purpose</h2>
<p>
  Prior-art grounding for the <strong>design-critique correction surface</strong>
  (<a href="/backlog/1036-plateau-review-surface-view-a-page-critique-comment-correct-/">backlog #1036</a>,
  under the interactive design-review epic
  <a href="/backlog/1033-interactive-design-review-loop-analyse-a-page-get-a-critique/">#1033</a>):
  the plateau-app surface that shows a page's auto-generated design critique, lets a human comment and
  correct it, and persists the result as a labeled <code>{frame, critique}</code> training pair — the
  corpus accumulator that un-parks the on-device verdict model (#513). Session report:
  <code>reports/2026-06-20-design-critique-correction-surface.md</code>.
</p>

